/td></tr><tr><td valign="top" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px;" width="108"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 14px;">可选配件</span></p></td><td valign="top" style="border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); padding: 0px 7px;" width="772"><p style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;"><span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">电子过滤扫描探头，基本款过滤扫描探头，</span>TSI<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">风速探头，温湿度探头，等动力探头，采样管，硬质便携箱，打印纸，浮游菌收集器，浮游菌收集过滤片，</span>FMS<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">软件</span></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">*BIO TRAK<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">实时浮游菌粒子计数器</span>9510-BD<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">型遵循以下技术专利；专利号：</span>6<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">，</span>167<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">，</span>107<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">；</span>5<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">，</span>701<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">，</span>012<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">；</span>5<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">，</span>895<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">，</span>922<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">；</span>6<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">，</span>831<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">，</span>279<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">；</span>7<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">，</span>261<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">，</span>007.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="font-size: 14px;">**<span style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体;">最高温度受限于凝胶过器</span></span></p><p style="line-height: 1.75em;"><span style="